FEATURES
- aspect ratio detection
- fullscreen mode
- controllerbar autohide
- preview image
- autoplay
- loop
- different colours via flashvars

MOVIE TYPES
- FLV, F4V
- MOV, MP4
- vimeo, youtube

CREATED WITH:
- Flash CS4
- De MonsterDebugger http://www.deMonsterDebugger.com
- TweenLite http://blog.greensock.com/tweenlite/
- moogaloop http://vimeo.com/api/docs/moogaloop
- youtube api http://blog.derhess.de/2009/10/27/the-new-youtube-as3-chromeless-api-in-flex-air-flash/